headline: TTD Stock Post Q3 Earnings: Should Investors Hold or Fold?
summary: TTD's shares have plunged after the third quarter despite upbeat results, as rising costs, fierce ad-tech competition and macro headwinds cloud its outlook.

headline: The Trade Desk (TTD) Fell Amid Strength in Broader Advertising Market
summary: Baron Funds, an investment management company, released its “Baron Technology Fund” third-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. US equities rallied in the third quarter following the previous quarter.
